articles.title: Aryna Sabalenka smashes racket in disgust after being upset by Madison Keys at Australian Open - New York Post
articles.description: Aryna Sabalenka saw her two-year reign at the Australian Open end after losing to Madison Keys in the final – and she didn’t take it well.
